<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #0a173b;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 150px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <!-- Header -->
    <div
      class="header"
      style="
        background-color: #0a173b;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
      "
    >
      <img
        src="https://va-claims-assets.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/VA_Claims_Main_Logo_Transparent_2_200px.png"
        alt="VA Claims Academy Logo"
        style="max-width: 100px; height: auto"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Email Body -->
    <div style="padding: 20px">
      <p style="font-size: 16px">Hi <%= name %>,</p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        We hope this email finds you well! We're reaching out because we're
        excited to connect with you and help you take a crucial step in your VA
        claims journey.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        We noticed that you haven't scheduled your discovery call yet.
        <strong style="color: #0a173b"
          >This call is a key opportunity for us to understand your unique
          situation and tailor our assistance to your specific needs.</strong
        >
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        <strong style="color: #0a173b"
          >Your story matters, and this call is your chance to share it with us.
          It's an important step towards building a stronger VA claim!</strong
        >
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        Ready to take this step? Just click the button below to schedule your
        discovery call at a time that works best for you:
      </p>

      <p style="text-align: center">
        <a
          href="<%= schedulingLink %>"
          style="
            background-color: #0a173b;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
          "
          >Schedule Your Discovery Call</a
        >
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        If you're having trouble finding a suitable time or have any questions,
        please don't hesitate to reach out. We're here to make this process as
        smooth as possible for you.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        We're looking forward to speaking with you and helping you navigate your
        VA claims journey!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div
      style="
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        padding-top: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      "
    >
      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        In your corner,<br />
        VA Claims Academy Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
